[Canada Post](https://www.canadapost.ca/tools/pg/manual/PGaddress-e.asp#1442131) and
[Statistique Canada](https://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2011/ref/dict/table-tableau/table-tableau-8-eng.cfm)

### Actual behavior

Generates inappropriate fake data with NV instead of NU.
