796,IssuesEvent,2018-02-08 15:58:21+00:00,6909307,gawel/pyquery,118673,gawel,,,closed,"In new version 1.4.0, when extract text which have newline, the newline character is omitted",[],[],4,"Hi, I found there are different behavior between 1.4.0 and previous version 1.3.0
