799,IssuesEvent,2016-06-23 08:44:58+00:00,6909307,gawel/pyquery,1736499,jjwt,,,opened,has not support eq(index) string in filter selector?,[],[],0,"it is found that .eq(index) selector works well as a outer selctor ,but not in filter string.
Below is test function

```python
def test_a():
    s = '''
    <html>
