1605,IssuesEvent,2017-11-14 19:37:30+00:00,1206729,hhatto/autopep8,308610,jaraco,,,opened,Replacing apply breaks when apply is global,[],[],0,"Consider this code:

```
$ cat > test-issue.py
def apply(a, b):
  return a

apply('x', 'b')
$ autopep8 -i --aggressive ./test-issue.py
$ cat test-issue.py                       
def apply(a, b):
    return a


('x')(*'b')
```

