1984,IssuesEvent,2018-03-06 20:25:27+00:00,3489194,davidhalter/jedi,748594,davidhalter,,,closed,test is installed,[],[],1,"This distribution trying to create a ""test"" subdirectory in site-packages and that's causing issues in some CI workflows.

