2769,IssuesEvent,2016-12-23 16:41:17+00:00,32283257,philpep/testinfra,6173051,jochenvdv,,,opened,Support Arch Linux,[],[],0,"It would be nice if the Package module could support Arch Linux (and its package manager Pacman).
