3329,IssuesEvent,2018-05-25 03:08:05+00:00,39159799,JoelBender/bacpypes,10273490,JoelBender,,,closed,BBMD request for ForeignApplication server,[],"[{'login': 'JoelBender', 'id': 10273490, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/10273490?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/JoelBender', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/JoelBender/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",2,"In previous issue (#166), I provided to you a patch to allow foreign device to reply to BBMD requests with Result messages. But according to the second issue (#167), we agreed that foreign application should reply to unicast requests even if no register response has been received.

Combining both of these ticket results, I found an issue in my previous patch regarding treatment of BBMD requests for foreign application which has not already received the registration confirmation.
BBMD requests are ignored because the `BIPForeign.confirmation` checks the registration validity before processing of BBMD requests. Then I suggest you to move the part regarding registration validity at the end of the `confirmation` method.

[0021_UnicastForBBMDRequest.txt](https://github.com/JoelBender/bacpypes/files/1836725/0021_UnicastForBBMDRequest.txt)
",{},{}
