3667,IssuesEvent,2018-08-31 20:05:27+00:00,3247274,niwinz/django-jinja,20211140,pykong,,,opened,How to use pyjade as an extension?,[],[],0,"Due to some major limitations of the `pyjade` implementation (See: https://github.com/syrusakbary/pyjade/issues/285), I thought a potential workaround might be to use `django-jinja` and configure `pyjade` as an extension. This approach is warranted due to pyjade working flawlessly in the context of Flask.

