7997,IssuesEvent,2015-12-12 00:42:06+00:00,648332,assimp/assimp,16262132,Styxsz,265533,assimp,opened,Memory leak when using Assimp,[],[],0,"So I've made a simple OpenGL application using Assimp for the model loading and I've noticed that my application is leaking some memory at startup. 

