8764,IssuesEvent,2018-02-23 18:06:26+00:00,79510167,pypa/pipenv,119893,kennethreitz,647025,pypa,closed,Pipenv uninstall doesn't uninstall dependencies,[],[],2,"When I run pipenv uninstall, I am counting on uninstalling the package with all it's dependencies that are not shared with other packages.

