8784,IssuesEvent,2018-04-12 20:12:24+00:00,79510167,pypa/pipenv,20703378,vyzyv,647025,pypa,closed,[DOCKER] Pipenv as base image crashes,[],[],2,"Image tagged latest fails as builder image.

------------

##### Expected result

Image builds normally.

##### Actual result

Crashes during pipenv install --deploy --system from your Dockerfile. Yesterday everything was fine.

```An error occurred while installing absl-py==0.1.13! Will try again.
An error occurred while installing absl-py==0.1.13! Will try again.
An error occurred while installing altgraph==0.15! Will try again.
An error occurred while installing astor==0.6.2! Will try again.
```

##### Steps to replicate

Create Dockerfile and use the latest as base image:

```
FROM kennethreitz/pipenv:latest AS builder
```

