9513,IssuesEvent,2016-09-06 15:34:57+00:00,40909583,inveniosoftware/invenio-search,587148,david-caro,1157480,inveniosoftware,opened,RFC allow overriding elasticsearch global timeout setting,[],[],0,"It would be really nice if that parameter (set to 10 secs by default on our current setup) could be configured, as sometimes we are finding timeout issues on busy and/or slow dev and test machines.

