11019,IssuesEvent,2018-08-06 20:27:18+00:00,30509483,clab/dynet,8679738,kwalcock,2374376,clab,opened,Windows build fails,[],[],0,"After the solution dynet.sln gets built, there are still quite a few problems.  After issue #1426 gets fixed, the next problem seems to be with this line from CMakeLists.txt.
