11598,IssuesEvent,2016-07-07 02:54:43+00:00,4086616,shadowsocks/shadowsocks,2255433,tarbib,3006190,shadowsocks,opened,"You can update ""setting a Shadowsocks relay""",[],[],0,"https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks/wiki/Setup-a-Shadowsocks-relay

This 

> global
>         ulimit-n  51200
> 
> defaults
>         log global
>         mode    tcp
>         option  dontlognull
>         contimeout 1000
>         clitimeout 150000
>         srvtimeout 150000
> 
> frontend ss-in
>         bind *:8388
>         default_backend ss-out
> 
> backend ss-out
>         server server1 US_VPS_IP:8388 maxconn 20480


should be replaced by :

> global
>         ulimit-n  51200
> 
> defaults
>         log     global
>         mode    tcp
>         option  dontlognull
>         timeout connect 1000
>         timeout client  150000
>         timeout server  150000
> 		
> frontend ss-in
>         bind *:8388
>         default_backend ss-out
> 
> backend ss-out
>         server server1 US_VPS_IP:8388 maxconn 20480",{},{}
