12786,IssuesEvent,2017-09-08 12:48:38+00:00,66922106,frictionlessdata/datapackage-pipelines,76945,vitorbaptista,5912125,frictionlessdata,opened,Running pipeline with unknown processor makes dpp fails silently,[],[],0,"Python 3.6 @ Ubuntu 16.04

