12907,IssuesEvent,2015-10-05 16:26:34+00:00,11589713,deis/deis,1821014,krancour,6117407,deis,closed,Stateless logger,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/deis/deis/labels/logger', 'name': 'logger', 'color': '009800'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/deis/deis/labels/open-roadmap', 'name': 'open-roadmap', 'color': '009800'}]",[],1,"Users who have elected to run a Ceph-less cluster (http://docs.deis.io/en/latest/managing_deis/running-deis-without-ceph/) give up application logs since ``deis-controller`` has nowhere to store them. To alleviate this, we plan to implement an in-memory ring buffer for the ``deis-logger`` component, so that a reasonable period of recent logs is stored and can be queried with ``deis logs``.",{},{}
