13312,IssuesEvent,2018-02-19 16:57:37+00:00,26839425,arista-eosplus/pyeapi,28887999,King-Joakim,6643264,arista-eosplus,opened,Add support for multiple/secondary Ip-addresses in ipinterfaces() function,[],[],0,"Hello, Im trying to get my secondary ip's configured from the api('ipinterfaces').get(interface) function, however it only returns the first it finds as per the **def _parse_address** function.

