15246,IssuesEvent,2015-04-17 20:21:25+00:00,4637221,powerline/powerline,322097,ZyX-I,10100576,powerline,closed,Unicode comparison warining,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/powerline/powerline/labels/c:b:vim', 'name': 'c:b:vim', 'color': '5379e7'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/powerline/powerline/labels/t:bug', 'name': 't:bug', 'color': 'FF0000'}]",[],4,"I installed powerline with [ctrlspace](https://github.com/szw/vim-ctrlspace) in vim. When I open the ctrlspace window, I got a warning said
```python
UnicodeWarning: Unicode equal comparison failed to convert both arguments to Unicode - interpreting them as being unequal
```

You may fix it easily by modifying the code at [line 244](https://github.com/powerline/powerline/blob/develop/powerline/vim.py#L244) of vim.py
```diff
- if window.options['statusline'] != statusline:
+ if type(window.options['statusline']) != type(statusline) or window.options['statusline'] != statusline:
```

