15331,IssuesEvent,2016-03-17 22:04:07+00:00,40094312,pyserial/pyserial,10556012,zsquareplusc,10537924,pyserial,closed,BUG: serialposix.py _set_rs485_mode() tries to read non-existing rs485_settings.delay_rts_before_send,[],[],1,"Hi,

