15698,IssuesEvent,2015-07-30 03:10:37+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,1303078,wanderseeme,11668813,Z3Prover,opened,Z3 CLI: crash on certain assertion checking (Int and Bool mix expression),[],[],0,"Say I have a file z3crash2.smt2 with content below:

(declare-datatypes () ((Tuple (tuple (first Int) (second Int)))))
(declare-const a Tuple)
(declare-const b Tuple)

(assert (= (first a) (distinct (first b) 0)))
(check-sat)

then I type ""z3 z3crash2.smt2"" in terminal, I get:

