16274,IssuesEvent,2017-01-24 10:17:26+00:00,43645564,ganga-devs/ganga,13677368,drmarkwslater,13271048,ganga-devs,opened,Change of behaviour for Dirac.getOutputDataLFNS?,"[{'id': 288695250, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/ganga-devs/ganga/labels/DIRAC', 'name': 'DIRAC', 'color': 'd4c5f9', 'default': False}]",[],0,"From 
