16716,IssuesEvent,2018-08-25 10:36:55+00:00,43056951,graphql-python/graphene,691952,jkimbo,15002022,graphql-python,closed,Support for Decimal type,[],[],3,"I've been using my own implementation of a Decimal type -- maybe it should be included as a standard type?


